# 5. 与 Pytest 集成

DeepEval 提供 `@pytest.mark.parametrize` 风格的数据驱动,推荐配合 golden dataset。

```python
# test_rag.py
import pytest
from deepeval import assert_test
from deepeval.test_case import LLMTestCase
from deepeval.metrics import FaithfulnessMetric, AnswerRelevancyMetric
from rag_min import build_rag   # 你的 RAG 系统

GOLDEN = [
    {"q": "怎么重启服务?", "expected": "使用 svc restart。"},
    {"q": "默认端口?", "expected": "默认端口 9101。"},
]

@pytest.fixture(scope="module")
def ask():
    return build_rag(["服务重启命令是 svc restart。默认端口 9101。"])

@pytest.mark.parametrize("item", GOLDEN, ids=lambda i: i["q"])
def test_rag(ask, item):
    answer, ctx = ask(item["q"])
    tc = LLMTestCase(
        input=item["q"], actual_output=answer,
        expected_output=item["expected"], retrieval_context=ctx,
    )
    assert_test(tc, [
        FaithfulnessMetric(threshold=0.7),
        AnswerRelevancyMetric(threshold=0.7),
    ])
```

运行:

```bash
deepeval test run test_rag.py            # DeepEval 专用 runner(推荐,有汇总报告)
deepeval test run test_rag.py -n 4       # 并行 4 进程加速
pytest test_rag.py                       # 也能直接用 pytest
```

